{"tid":425480,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"掛住一個唔再屬於你嘅人","createTime":"2017-10-05T18:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T05:34:09.000Z","uid":76010,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"59e690c3e57c2a5b1be7705a66b8bb885c4e3af4","tid":425480,"uid":76010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T18:16:22.000Z","msg":"有冇人飛完人之後， 開心咗一排，但原來其實自己仲都好掛住佢。但係佢而家已經做咗人哋女朋友。就算你掛住佢 ，佢哋一世都唔會再知道你掛住佢。<br />\n<br />\n所以咁多位巴打唔好因為一時嘅衝動而做出 一世後悔嘅決定，記得珍惜眼前人。"},{"pid":"3e5d11e9cc2cd23367024da1dc159e505fc84c88","tid":425480,"uid":145987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T19:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33cdf6d13b615828accb948e8660d841a67ec506","tid":425480,"uid":561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T19:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11beb76fd30c682db6cb527b80010d326423009","tid":425480,"uid":137847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T20:10:36.000Z","msg":"雖然佢未係屬於我<br />\n<br />\n但心中思念<br />\n佢永遠唔會知"},{"pid":"0a3edce3db4dc38e23cf6dd46a97dfb8373b05a2","tid":425480,"uid":13467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T20:17:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然佢未係屬於我<br />\n<br />\n但心中思念<br />\n佢永遠唔會知</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iHqXnYtM7NI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiHqXnYtM7NI&d=zIzVymQCCpWUAERTiXoeB9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=07834547\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iHqXnYtM7NI</a><br />\n對方心怎樣在跳 或你根本不會知"},{"pid":"b9ef1af59b7069e97ea06771c0ed206f71591111","tid":425480,"uid":151780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s